{"tid":778191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實廢老做野真係好撚慢","createTime":"2018-08-13T13:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T13:31:35.000Z","uid":12007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dc52a160813f6d5f75a95390394ca8949f1ec84a","tid":778191,"uid":12007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"朝早食大家樂，出餐成條team都係50-60歲d呀嬸，唔明點解出個早餐都可以亂左唔知邊份係邊個，最on9係刷鞋做埋送餐比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就係咁等餐都要排成15個<br />\n到岩岩食麥當勞，得一個呀嬸係counter 篤機，又係唔知咩事比人屌，然後人地排隊問題都要插咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係話歧視佢地，但佢地本身就不思進取，稍為有少少科技野就唔撚識花大把時間去教！篤機都唔識篤，篤錯又搵返經理，有客屌又搵經理，班經理又on9掉一個廢老出邊篤機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔離post話m記無哂靚女做呢樣真，靚女做野通常好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2518cf19e9abcb7de6c238657a37f9a163f025d","tid":778191,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />番工果度啲廢老做野妹下妹下 轉個身都慢過人 明知我地忙都慢慢泥 阻住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 念在佢係我前輩先唔一野煎巴佢"},{"pid":"7fb9127441d21e8219fcfd2c58668683c17d176c","tid":778191,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"做咁快手做乜 有得分咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}